keyMappings:
# match vim "seek" plugins
#  "f": "LinkHints.activateMode",
#  "F": "LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab",
#  "<a-f>": "LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue",
#  "yf": "LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl",
map s LinkHints.activateMode
map S LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
# map <a-s> LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue # mac alt
map ys LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
unmap f
unmap F
# unmap <a-f>
unmap yf

# rebind go to tab to ctr + p
unmap T
map <c-p> Vomnibar.activateTabSelection

# fix mac alt keys
unmap <a-p>
map <a-π> togglePinTab
unmap <a-f>
map <a-ß> LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
unmap <a-m>
map <a-µ> toggleMuteTab
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
